videos.description: Horace Spencer blocks a layup allowing Davion Mitchell to hit a triple on the other end.
videos.headline: Auburn turns block into Mitchell 3-pointer

videos.description: Donta Hall protects the rim with a big rejection on an Auburn layup attempt.
videos.headline: Hall rises up for big block for Alabama

videos.description: After a Tigers steal, Jared Harper throws up a lob to Mustapha Heron who jams it home.
videos.headline: Harper connects with Heron for Auburn alley-oop

videos.description: Bryce Brown tosses up a perfect lob pass to Mustapha Heron who goes up and gets it for a big jam.
videos.headline: Auburn's steal leads to powerful alley-oop

videos.description: Chuma Okeke drains a 3-pointer as the first half ends to give Auburn a three-point lead at halftime.
videos.headline: Okeke's 3-pointer just beats halftime buzzer

videos.description: After getting a steal, Herbert Jones goes all the way for a lay-in and a foul.
videos.headline: Jones turns steal into and-1 layup for Alabama

videos.description: Daniel Giddens hammers down a big dunk over an Auburn defender.
videos.headline: Giddens punishes the rim with big dunk

videos.description: Alex Reese misses a 3-pointer but Donta Hall rises up to jam it home.
videos.headline: Hall jams home putback dunk for Alabama
